Reference -

https://impala.apache.org/docs/build/html/topics/impala_perf_hdfs_caching.html

https://hadoop.apache.org/docs/stable/hadoop-project-dist/hadoop-hdfs/CentralizedCacheManagement.html

hdfs cacheadmin -addPool <pool name> -owner impala -limit 4000000000


hdfs cacheadmin -listPools

hdfs cacheadmin -modifyPool <pool name> -maxTtl 30m

hdfs cacheadmin -listPools
